{
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.title": "Mithrix",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.firstVisitEver.0-0.ancient": "Greetings, vermin.",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.epithet": "King of Nothing",
  
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.ANY.0-0r.ancient": "You return? How vile.",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.ANY.1-0r.ancient": "We meet again. Take my blessing and go, vermin.",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.ANY.2-0r.ancient": "Tireless, you are. It will not matter.",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.ANY.3-0r.ancient": "Ah, another pest has arrived to claim a treasure.",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.ANY.4-0r.ancient": "Take this, vermin, and embrace design.",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.ANY.5-0r.ancient": "Another vermin? Take a bauble, and be on your way.",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.ANY.6-0r.ancient": "Your spirit will crumble eventually. Until then, claim your boon, vermin.",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.ANY.7-0r.ancient": "I see you still fight relentlessly. Perhaps I should simply strike you down myself. It would be mercy.",

  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.IRONCLAD.0-0r.ancient": "Welcome, infernal pest.",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.IRONCLAD.0-0r.next": "Continue",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.IRONCLAD.0-1r.char": "[i][font_size=22]The Ironclad brandishes their blade.[/font_size][/i]",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.IRONCLAD.0-1r.next": "Continue",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.IRONCLAD.0-2r.ancient": "Cease your struggling and take a boon, wretch.",

  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.IRONCLAD.1-0r.ancient": "Vermin, why do you persist on this quest?",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.IRONCLAD.1-0r.next": "Continue",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.IRONCLAD.1-1r.char": "[i][font_size=22]The Ironclad points their sword upwards.[/font_size][/i]",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.IRONCLAD.1-1r.next": "Continue",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.IRONCLAD.1-2r.ancient": "Slay the Architect? How foolish. You remind me of my brother.",

  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.SILENT.0-0r.ancient": "Another vermin to climb the spire?",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.SILENT.0-0r.next": "Say Nothing",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.SILENT.0-1r.char": "...",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.SILENT.0-1r.next": "Continue",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.SILENT.0-2r.ancient": "No rude remarks? You are more tolerable than the other vermin.",

  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.SILENT.1-0r.ancient": "You persist despite being so frail and weak?",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.SILENT.1-0r.next": "Say Nothing",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.SILENT.1-1r.char": "...",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.SILENT.1-1r.next": "Continue",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.SILENT.1-2r.ancient": "Take your baubles and trinkets, vermin. You will shatter soon enough.",

  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.REGENT.0-0r.ancient": "Such eccentric garbs for a mere vermin.",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.REGENT.0-0r.next": "Scold",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.REGENT.0-1r.char": "Vermin!? You disrespect the heir to the Throne of Stars!",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.REGENT.0-1r.next": "Continue",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.REGENT.0-2r.ancient": "No vermin deserves a throne.",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.REGENT.0-2r.next": "Talk",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.REGENT.0-3r.char": "I should smite you where you stand, but I will show you mercy! Offer to me a gift and I will be on my way!",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.REGENT.0-3r.next": "Continue",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.REGENT.0-4r.ancient": "If it will silence you, then so be it.",
  
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.REGENT.1-0r.ancient": "The king of the vermin returns.",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.REGENT.1-0r.next": "Respond",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.REGENT.1-1r.char": "Insolent fool! Have you any idea who I am?",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.REGENT.1-1r.next": "Continue",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.REGENT.1-2r.ancient": "An ignorant pest who doesn't know their place.",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.REGENT.1-2r.next": "Challenge",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.REGENT.1-3r.char": "If I am a mere pest to you, then face me!",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.REGENT.1-3r.next": "Continue",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.REGENT.1-4r.ancient": "You aren't worth my time, vermin. Take a treasure and begone.",

  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.NECROBINDER.0-0r.ancient": "Blood and soul course through your essence. What have you done, conjurer?",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.NECROBINDER.0-0r.next": "Respond",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.NECROBINDER.0-1r.char": "My actions aren't your business.",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.NECROBINDER.0-1r.next": "Continue",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.NECROBINDER.0-2r.ancient": "So be it.",

  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.NECROBINDER.1-0r.ancient": "Who pulls your strings, conjurer?",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.NECROBINDER.1-0r.next": "Talk",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.NECROBINDER.1-1r.char": "Revenge for my family. He will pay for what he's done.",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.NECROBINDER.1-1r.next": "Continue",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.NECROBINDER.1-2r.ancient": "Do not regret this journey, being of memories.",

  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.DEFECT.0-0r.ancient": "A construct? Born of soul...disgusting.",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.DEFECT.0-0r.next": "Reply",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.DEFECT.0-1r.char": "[i][font_size=22]<angry beeps>[/font_size][/i]",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.DEFECT.0-1r.next": "Continue",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.DEFECT.0-2r.ancient": "Take your boon and begone from here, wretch.",

  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.DEFECT.1-0r.ancient": "What manner of sculptor created you, construct?",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.DEFECT.1-0r.next": "Reply",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.DEFECT.1-1r.char": "[i][font_size=22]<displeased beeps>[/font_size][/i]",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.DEFECT.1-1r.next": "Continue",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.DEFECT.1-2r.ancient": "The Architect? I see. So this is your business with them.",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.DEFECT.1-2r.next": "Reply",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.DEFECT.1-3r.char": "[i][font_size=22]<affirmative beep boop>[/font_size][/i]",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.DEFECT.1-3r.next": "Continue",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-MITHRIX_ANCIENT.talk.DEFECT.1-4r.ancient": "Perhaps not all constructs of soul are as vile as the Guardian once was.",


  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-LESHY_ANCIENT.title": "Leshy",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-LESHY_ANCIENT.epithet": "Scrybe of Beasts",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-LESHY_ANCIENT.talk.firstVisitEver.0-0.ancient": "Welcome. Please, have a seat.",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-LESHY_ANCIENT.talk.firstVisitEver.0-0.next": "Continue",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-LESHY_ANCIENT.talk.firstVisitEver.0-1.ancient": "You are welcome to take one of my relics, but first, how about a round of cards?",

  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-LESHY_ANCIENT.talk.ANY.0-0r.ancient": "Welcome back. Would you care to play a round?",


  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-SEBASTIAN_ANCIENT.title": "Sebastian",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-SEBASTIAN_ANCIENT.epithet": "Disgraced Handyman",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-SEBASTIAN_ANCIENT.talk.firstVisitEver.0-0.ancient": "Welcome, welcome! Care to pick up one of these... \"loose assets\" I've found?~",

  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-SEBASTIAN_ANCIENT.talk.ANY.0-0r.ancient": "Oh hey! Check it, I was going around the Hive, lots of goodies. I found your body, and some of your relics were still intact!",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-SEBASTIAN_ANCIENT.talk.ANY.0-0r.next": "Continue",
  "ANCIENTSAWAKENED-SEBASTIAN_ANCIENT.talk.ANY.0-1r.ancient": "Hey, don't worry about it, you can have them back....for a price~"
}